data.title: CAC:Central Arizona College
data.meta_description: Central Arizona College is a community college with 5 convenient locations in Pinal county dedicated to accessibility, excellence and affordability. Call 520-494-5111.
data.text:
Central Arizona College Invites New Students to Orientation Sessions in August

CAC invites new students, along with their family, supporters and other guests to attend New Student Orientations prior to the start of the fall semester.

CAC Foundation to Host Golf Tournament Fundraiser

The Central Arizona College Foundation is hosting a golf tournament on Friday, Nov. 8, 2024.
